          %h4 What Is It?
          %p
            Project Jellyfish is a community-driven open source cloud broker that unifies disparate cloud services across multiple private, public and hybrid cloud infrastructure, resulting in automated and rapid service delivery, comprehensive performance and cost monitoring, standardized configuration management, and customizable workflows. Project Jellyfish is built by an open community of developers, designers and end users. Learn how you can contribute to this growing community.
